author: The Current
description:
Watch Samia and her band perform "Bovine Excision" off 'Bloodless' 
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Singer-songwriter Samia releases her second full-length album, 'Bloodless,' on April 25, 2025. Just a few weeks before the release, Samia visited The Current studio with some of her musical collaborators to perform four songs off the new album. Here's their performance of "Bovine Excision."

Samia’s 2025 album, Bloodless, is available on @grandjurymusic.

Musicians
Samia Finnerty – vocals
Sam Rosenstone – keyboards, vocals
Jake Luppen – electric guitar, vocals
Nathan Stocker – six- and 12-string guitar, vocals

Credits
Guest – @samiatheband 
Host – Jessica Paxton
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Audio – Evan Clark
Video – Derek Ramirez
Camera Operators – Derek Ramirez, Ruben Schneiderman
Graphics – Natalia Toledo
Digital Producer – Luke Taylor

author: The Current
description:
The Current's Jessica Paxton talks to Samia about the album, 'Bloodless'
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube 

Singer-songwriter Samia releases her second full-length album, 'Bloodless,' on April 25, 2025. Just a few weeks before the release, Samia visited The Current studio with some of her musical collaborators to perform four songs off the new album. Afterwards, Samia sat down with The Current’s Jessica Paxton to talk about 'Bloodless' and also to talk about what inspired her to move to Minneapolis from New York City. Watch and listen to interview above.

Samia’s 2025 album, 'Bloodless,' is available on @grandjurymusic.

Watch to see the full session of Dan Wilson, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when he visited the The Current studio back in 2014.
